title: Avolon delivers one Boeing 737-800 to Aeromexico
text:
Avolon delivers one Boeing 737-800 to Aeromexico Adv: 
Jul 30, 2015 Adv: 
DUBLIN, Ireland - Avolon, the international aircraft leasing company, today announces the delivery of a third Boeing 737-800 to Aeromexico. The delivery is the third of four Boeing 737-800 aircraft scheduled for delivery to Aeromexico by Avolon.
